creator: Appyhigh Technology
descriptionHtml:
Masterfeed, India's first AI-powered feed app for local and national news, social media platforms, videos, short videos, podcasts and all your content needs.

Personalised feed
Get a feed as interesting & unique as you. Our AI based recommendation engine will curate a feed of news, social media trends, videos, and reels based on your likes, dislikes and interests.
Master of all feeds is here to serve you, so you won’t need to go anywhere else.

Latest News Updates
Follow national and local news updates as they happen. Get access to world, national and regional news all at one place

Multiple Categories
We cover content and news from Sports,Business, Astrology, Horoscope, Celebrity Gossips,Podcasts, Business to Education. Just dive in a category and explore it all.

See what’s trending
Follow what;s trending on social media such as Twitter, Instagram or Facebook. From viral tweets to share worthy memes, Masterfeed app is your one size fits all solution.

Content Superapp
Content made simple.Masterfeed,India's 1st intelligent social & news feed. We give you content superapp curated by experts.
We deliver handpicked, reliable content in every shape and format sourced from all nooks and corners of the country.Whether you prefer to get your news from a reputed publications desk. Or like to hear it right out of the horse’s mouth from stringers and local reporters. Or want a sense of the nation’s pulse through interesting user-generated content. Or prefer visuals over text. Or like to hear your news on the go. We got it all covered in MasterFeed

Available in 15 Indian languages
Get your content and news in your local language. We offer you content in more than 10 languages and news from our local partners.
Get news from your favorite channels as Live Hindustan, Aaj Tak, Amar Ujala,Jagran, Prabhat Khabar, Punjab Kesari

Masterfeed features
1. 15+ vernacular support
2. Access to world, national and regional news all at one place
3. Multiple formats supported like articles, gallery, videos, stories, live feed, short-videos, podcasts and more
4. Streaming content ie. TV, movies aggregated from all OTT platforms and suggested as per user's proclivity
5. Rich user generated content from influencers, opinion leaders and general public
6. Local and National Job Updates

title: MasterFeed- News, Videos on all topics, Daily News

creator: Appyhigh Technology
descriptionHtml:
Masterfeed, India's first AI-powered feed app for local and national news, social media platforms, videos, short videos, podcasts and all your content needs.

Personalised feed
Get a feed as interesting & unique as you. Our AI based recommendation engine will curate a feed of news, social media trends, videos, and reels based on your likes, dislikes and interests.
Master of all feeds is here to serve you, so you won’t need to go anywhere else.

Latest News Updates
Follow national and local news updates as they happen. Get access to world, national and regional news all at one place

Multiple Categories
We cover content and news from Sports,Business, Astrology, Horoscope, Celebrity Gossips,Podcasts, Business to Education. Just dive in a category and explore it all.

See what’s trending
Follow what;s trending on social media such as Twitter, Instagram or Facebook. From viral tweets to share worthy memes, Masterfeed app is your one size fits all solution.

Content Superapp
Content made simple.Masterfeed,India's 1st intelligent social & news feed. We give you content superapp curated by experts.
We deliver handpicked, reliable content in every shape and format sourced from all nooks and corners of the country.Whether you prefer to get your news from a reputed publications desk. Or like to hear it right out of the horse’s mouth from stringers and local reporters. Or want a sense of the nation’s pulse through interesting user-generated content. Or prefer visuals over text. Or like to hear your news on the go. We got it all covered in MasterFeed

Available in 15 Indian languages
Get your content and news in your local language. We offer you content in more than 10 languages and news from our local partners.
Get news from your favorite channels as Live Hindustan, Aaj Tak, Amar Ujala,Jagran, Prabhat Khabar, Punjab Kesari

Masterfeed features
1. 15+ vernacular support
2. Access to world, national and regional news all at one place
3. Multiple formats supported like articles, gallery, videos, stories, live feed, short-videos, podcasts and more
4. Streaming content ie. TV, movies aggregated from all OTT platforms and suggested as per user's proclivity
5. Rich user generated content from influencers, opinion leaders and general public
6. Local and National Job Updates
